data.description: This gorgeous updated home is the epitome of the perfect location! Just minutes from Baybrook mall, countless other shopping destinations, dining options, and fun activities; while still being in a quiet and friendly neighborhood!  As soon as you walk in you're greeted by a beautiful flex space that flows right into the open living area. With updated granite counter tops, plenty of natural light, washer/dryer included, and surround sound/projector+pull down screen in the primary, this place is ready for all your entertainment needs! Don't forget the brand new deck outside for the best nights and cozy mornings. Tour today because this one is going fast!
